Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜宵的蛋糕做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神哥哥大人  請等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的那個是意外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微把小麥粉的用量搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人間  就算是這樣的蛋糕也不會爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對這個世界的事情太不瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微給我去學一下一般常識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓我說多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今的搭檔角色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.19,0:02:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知性和個性是必須的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.65,0:02:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼神大人就是我現今的搭檔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別從你的角度來看！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是搭檔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有在好好學習的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人間的事情也學習過了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本史可是「優」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:02:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是日本博士哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便問下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候你最後學到的歷史是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是黑船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑船過來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑色的船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我開國
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是…這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在操場邊上有個圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在那裡學習一下這個世界的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的學校真是什麼都有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  開始學習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般常識…  一般常識…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級very bad…  KY…  now在young中很受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先…先從更簡單一點的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通紅的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消防車…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的時代有這種車在跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消防車來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是消防車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紅色的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想知道更多關於這車的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消防車
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消防車
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消防車…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消防…車
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消防…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候  就該去問接待的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這一樣的書在哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打…打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有什麼事找在下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書裡的台詞…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  還有其他刊登消防車的書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放學後…再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學以後嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩的身體裡有驅魂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ka  Mi  No  Mi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啵啵啵  鴿子  啵啵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要豆子嗎  來  給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PFP用軟體  嘉音的挑戰書
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最新發售
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teito
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ka  Mi  No  Mi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這邊  是這邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對圖書管理員的女孩有反應了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去圖書館都已經厭倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近在遊戲裡絕對會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書管理員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為大多數學校裡都有圖書館呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以那裡為據點的角色的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現地點也會受到限制  事件也容易編寫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的圖書管理員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是校園戀愛遊戲裡不可缺少的激戰區中的激戰區啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是相當優秀的傢伙的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可提不起半點幹勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不是很優秀…的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她沒有馬上告訴我消防車的書在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消防車？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  如果是半吊子的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就會送抗議的用戶調查表去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄到哪去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個圖書館裡刊登著消防車的書  全都在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共有…458本
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這邊為止都是以消防車為主題的書
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一本裡有消防車的插畫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一本是一位叫根津的警察所回憶的火災片段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的圖書館  有個很厲害的搜索啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為基本上我都記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我把這個圖書館裡的書全都看過了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:10:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事可不能說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是說出來的話  會被人討厭的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拿了這麼多的消防車的書  這又算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才更會讓人討厭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許兩三本就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要再問一下「你想看什麼樣的消防車呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  事到如今才…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個寡言的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅長與人接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有書本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在這裡  我就沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直  活在這個城堡中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又好像又是一個難題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  你都學了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡書本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一本書  都是一個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同語言的  不同的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一個書架  都是一個宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限延伸的  空想的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在這裡  我就能到任何地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成為任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本是紙與文字  再由人演奏的大合奏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越遙遠的時間  能夠傳達思念的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本是藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本是文化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本是時代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本是生命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本是太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本是歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本是人生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本是約定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本是風
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本是海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:14:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本是星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本是心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.49,0:15:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本是愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本是喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本是感動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天與書共渡的時光又開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正屬於我的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐宮栞  二年C班  12月26日出生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.32,0:15:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血型為B型  圖書管理員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個非常寡言的女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這種女孩能搞好關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  擔任圖書管理員的女生都有一個鐵則
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:15:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵則？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要側耳傾聽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會聽到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文系少女的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文系女生雖然文靜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但腦裡想的要比別人多一倍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和嘰嘰喳喳但腦袋空空的正好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種內在的兩面性  就是文系少女的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內向！  知性！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後就是文系少女的時代啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  要怎樣才能聽到內心的聲音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你是外行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心的聲音隨時都能聽見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  這是遊戲裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就無法攻略了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下次要來我家看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等不知廉恥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可是滿足求知慾的神聖之地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是兩位打情罵俏的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如古語有言「男女七歲後不應同席而坐」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確的男女交往應該是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐宮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  這個能拜託你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下來有事要去教員室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  等我的好消息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  書本們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們很快就要離開這個圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的去別的圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的去舊書店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  有的要去…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本既是紙亦非紙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是積累而成的智慧的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然這麼簡單地就被扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人  好像是昨天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛是在幫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱心嗎  真熱心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過為什麼幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這很正常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  該向他道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  普通地說就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.40,0:20:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起普通  還是更輕鬆的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  不過昨天見過面了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:21:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先加一句「昨天謝謝你了」比較好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先模擬一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  昨天也見過面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能已經忘記我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.58,0:21:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  又要在猶豫之中錯過時機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點說些什麼  快道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝論…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲裡沒有無果而終的戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.94,0:23:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從青梅竹馬到藝人  從學生會長到義妹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.54,0:23:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是女神是天使還是惡魔  只要有FLAG就是我的囊中物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.85,0:23:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說有例外…說不定就是…愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.16,0:23:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是BUG呢  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神哥哥大人  蛋糕做好嘍
